---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE } from "@/consts";
---

<Layout title="Get Involved | RealityFoundation" description="Join us in advancing research on AI-generated counterfeits and media authenticity. Multiple ways to contribute.">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 pt-18">
        <div class="space-y-20 py-12">
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <section class="space-y-6">
                <h1 class="heading text-4xl md:text-6xl uppercase">Get involved</h1>
                <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                        RealityFoundation is in its founding phase. We are actively building the team,
                        the research programme, and the network of partners that will define the
                        foundation's first years. There are multiple ways to contribute, depending on
                        who you are and what you bring.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Audience Segments Grid -->
            <section class="space-y-8 border-t border-secondary pt-12">
                <h2 class="heading text-4xl uppercase mb-12">How you can contribute</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                    <!-- Researchers and Doctoral Students -->
                    <div class="border border-secondary p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="heading text-xl uppercase text-primary">Researchers & doctoral students</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            We offer researchers the opportunity to publish under the RealityFoundation
                            umbrella, with editorial support, cross-citation within a growing body of
                            work, and visibility with policymakers and institutions who follow our outputs.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            If you are working on a thesis or research project related to fake detection,
                            synthetic media, AI governance, or media integrity, we would like to discuss
                            how we can support your work.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block text-primary font-semibold uppercase text-xs hover:underline"
                        >
                            Contact us about research opportunities →
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Professors and Academic Supervisors -->
                    <div class="border border-secondary p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="heading text-xl uppercase text-primary">Professors & academic supervisors</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            We are forming our Scientific Committee and building a network of academic
                            advisors. Involvement offers the opportunity to shape a research agenda at
                            the intersection of computer vision, AI ethics, digital forensics, and public policy.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            We can offer positions on the Scientific Committee, co-supervision arrangements
                            for thesis students, and a growing platform for research influence.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block text-primary font-semibold uppercase text-xs hover:underline"
                        >
                            Contact us about academic collaboration →
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Universities and Research Institutions -->
                    <div class="border border-secondary p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="heading text-xl uppercase text-primary">Universities & research institutions</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            We are seeking institutional partnerships with European universities and
                            research centres. If your institution works on topics related to our research
                            agenda, we are open to discussing collaboration.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            We can explore memoranda of understanding, joint research initiatives, and
                            student exchange arrangements.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block text-primary font-semibold uppercase text-xs hover:underline"
                        >
                            Contact us about institutional partnerships →
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Journalists and Media Organisations -->
                    <div class="border border-secondary p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="heading text-xl uppercase text-primary">Journalists & media organisations</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            Our research is designed to be useful to journalists and newsrooms grappling
                            with the challenge of synthetic media. We are available for comment, background
                            briefings, and longer-form collaborations.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            We can support investigations related to AI counterfeiting and media integrity.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block text-primary font-semibold uppercase text-xs hover:underline"
                        >
                            Press enquiries →
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Donors and Supporters -->
                    <div class="border border-secondary p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="heading text-xl uppercase text-primary">Donors & supporters</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            As a nonprofit, RealityFoundation depends on the support of individuals and
                            organisations who share our conviction that media authenticity is a public
                            good worth defending.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            If you are interested in supporting our work financially, we would welcome
                            a conversation about how you can make an impact.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block text-primary font-semibold uppercase text-xs hover:underline"
                        >
                            Get in touch →
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Institutions and Policymakers -->
                    <div class="border border-secondary p-8 rounded-lg hover:border-primary transition space-y-4">
                        <h3 class="heading text-xl uppercase text-primary">Institutions & policymakers</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            We engage actively with public institutions, regulators, and civil society
                            organisations working on AI governance and digital rights.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            If you are involved in policy work in this space and would like to explore
                            collaboration or commission research, please reach out.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block text-primary font-semibold uppercase text-xs hover:underline"
                        >
                            Contact us →
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Why Join Section -->
            <section class="space-y-8 border-t border-secondary pt-12">
                <h2 class="heading text-4xl uppercase">Why contribute?</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <h3 class="heading text-lg uppercase">Research impact</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            Be part of an independent foundation addressing one of the most urgent
                            technical and social challenges of our time.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <h3 class="heading text-lg uppercase">Policy influence</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            Your work reaches policymakers, regulators, and institutions who shape
                            the future of AI governance and digital rights.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <h3 class="heading text-lg uppercase">Community</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                            Join a network of researchers, practitioners, and thought leaders committed
                            to media authenticity and AI integrity.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <section class="space-y-8 border-t border-secondary pt-12">
                <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="heading text-3xl uppercase">Ready to get involved?</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-secondary">
                        Reach out to learn more about opportunities that match your background and
                        interests. We respond to all inquiries.
                    </p>
                    <div>
                        <a
                            href="/contact"
                            class="inline-block px-6 py-3 border border-primary text-primary font-semibold uppercase hover:bg-primary hover:text-black transition"
                        >
                            Contact us
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
